{
  "stem": "21582.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and the, the train was-- I don't know how many cars, but there were several.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At some point-- the, the distance from, from Majdanek to Skarzysko, I don't know how far it is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But, but it was quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At some point, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told us to go out in the field if we have to use the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, my sister had to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were saying, oh, Frieda, try not to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because if we go out, they'll probably shoot us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She says, but I have to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they rushed us back into the trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we got on, on another train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, as it worked out, when we got into, into Skarzysko, there were three camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was [NON-ENGLISH] A, B, and C.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], which is [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 'camp.' I, I can't think of the translation right now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they were three different camps, were three-- they, all three of them, were labor camps and ammunition factories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But in one, I think it was [NON-ENGLISH] C-- [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] A, B, and C.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] C was producing only the gunpowder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Before the war, when you worked there, you could-- you only worked a, a couple of hours maybe a day, and only at a very short periods of time because the gunpowder discolored your skin.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it also was toxic for your lungs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It, it, it, it settled on your lungs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was-- that was like a death camp because they worked the Jews there until they expired.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
